snippet.title: Prisms and Pyramids [ACT 3]: How Many Cones Does It Take To Fill a Cylinder?
snippet.description:
http://tapintoteenminds.com/3act-math/prisms-and-pyramids/ 
Learn about the relationship between cones and cylinders.  How many of the pyramids will it take to fill up the prism?  This video will answer that question for you.

This is the third act of a 3 act math task called "Prisms and Pyramids"
